The 59 F250 is a runner! Here's a video of the first time it has run in 30 years! Last registered in 91.
Via @mid_century_motors

node.text:
The Original @QruisinPCH Quarantine Cruise - QC:18: “Summer Bash” is set SUNDAY August 15th.

Title Sponsor: @fitech_efi
Presented by @classicperform

The Largest Monthly Cruise is hitting the OC Coast and ready to Party in HB! 
Come share the experience at two of our most popular locations alongside hundreds of incredible rides and car enthusiasts on the SoCal coast.

Details Drop Friday 8/13 at 5:00 p.m. (PST)

Featured in Motor Trend, Hot Rod, Truck Trend, Classic Truck Performance, All Chevy Performance, Dub magazine and across the internet, there’s no experience like the Quarantine Cruise.
_

@TheDaveCastle - Our local supporting realtor 🏡

_
Don’t miss out on the fun! Text “Cruise” to 21000 and stop by often to be 1st to know the details!
_
Respect the locations. Leave them as you found them.
NO BURNOUTS!
_
#hbqc
#quarantinecruise
_
Partners: @Hektattoo @keystoneautomotiveoperations @week2wickedjason @Ken
